Yale University

Compilation
===========
To compile the source, please run:
    $ make -C src

Three directories will be created: bin/, obj/ and logs/.

Running the Demo
================
In order to run the game you want to, from the root directory simply type:
    $ bin/[GAME_NAME]
    $ bin/Sudoku        # This will run Sudoku

To run the option selector (so that you may choose among the games) please run:
    $ bin/TheGame
